HEADWORD: Candle power
<hw>Candle power</hw></mhw>.
<fld>(Photom.)</fld> <def>luminous intensity; illuminating power, as of
a lamp, or gas flame, measured in candelas, referring to the light of a
standard candle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

